  "title": "ISic001984. Votive inscription to the goddess Astarte",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EGNUE9CZ\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EGNUE9CZ</a></div><div id=\"edition-interpretive-transliteration\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>lrbt lʿš <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>trt [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..</span>] b <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] b [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..</span>] d [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">..</span>] <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] ʿ gm <span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span></span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Jonathan Prag; edition source: <a href=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EGNUE9CZ\">http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/EGNUE9CZ</a></div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic-transliteration\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"xpu-Latn\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>LRBTLʿŠ<span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>TRT[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]B<span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]B[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]D[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">··</span>]<span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span><br id=\"al4-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>[<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>]ʿGM<span class=\"tei text-direction r-to-l\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;←</span></span></div><p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div></div>  <div id=\"facsimile-images\"><h2>Facsimile Images</h2><a href=\"ISic001984_tiled.tif\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001984_tiled-thumb.tif\"></a><a href=\"ISic001984.jpg\"><img title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001984-thumb.jpg\"></a></div>  <div id=\"apparatus\"><h4>Apparatus criticus</h4><ul><li><span><span>Text of De Simone 2013</span></span></li></ul></div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>English translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7393-1952\">Rossana De Simone</a></p>  <p>To the Lady, to Ashtarte .. b....... b.d.……. ʿ gm</p>  </div>  <div id=\"translation\"><h2>Italian translation</h2><p class=\"translation-author\"><a href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0002-7393-1952\">Rossana De Simone</a></p>  <p>Alla Signora, ad Astarte .. b...... b.d........ ʿ gm</p>  </div>  <div id=\"commentary\"><h2>commentary</h2>  <p>Only the first two lines of the inscription are interpretable; the rest is illegible due to the stone's poor state of preservation.</p>  </div>  <div id=\"bibliography\"><h2>bibliography</h2>  <ul><li> Coacci Polselli 1978 167-168, tav. LXXXV.1 </li><li> De Simone 2013 25 MO.1 fig.1 <a href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002545\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10002545</a>  </li></ul>  <ul><li></li></ul>  </div>  <div id=\"handnote\"> Line 1-4  21-76  Interlineation line 1 to 2    </div><div id=\"license\"> Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. </div>",
